data.description: Seeking a picturesque lake view? Look no further! This delightful residence offers breathtaking lake views from the front courtyard. Boasting 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a versatile den/office area, this home provides ample space for both family and friends. The home's spacious kitchen and living area create an ideal setting for entertaining. The generous backyard offers potential for a pool, casita, or maybe even both.  Plus there is ample space for side parking. Adding to your privacy, the property backs onto a serene wash. Notably, this home operates on a septic system for cost-effective water bills and features solar panels for energy efficiency. What more could one desire? Call today to arrange your exclusive viewing of this exceptional property.
